<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: black;
      color: white;
    }
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;
      background-image: url('/public/lang-logo.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 4em;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-weight: normal;
    }
    .cta {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .cta a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      border: 2px solid white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
    .cta a:hover {
      background-color: white;
      color: black;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Every Transaction Counts</h1>
    <p>Doconomy partners with financial institutions to drive positive impact on a global scale by offering innovative banking tools supported by human-centric design, behavioral science, and superior data.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="#">About Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Doconomy.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
